**Please read before download:
Sorry about a little over-sized release. It's because the movie is 2:45 long, and it has many action scenes which I didn't want to lose its details. But believe me the this brought a higher quality release so enjoy.

The source was ORIGINAL BluRay(41GB) so it makes the quality even better. what's important is, the movie has 2channel original AC3 from BluRay. But if you like the 6channel sound, I've included another audio file which you can download separately if you like. this is done for people which prefer to download 2ch sound which is about 750mb less size. If you like this way, I could do this for other releases too. you can just drag-drop the sound to the player after you load the movie or you can use mkvmerge to attach 6ch audio to original movie. The 6channel audio is also UNTOUCHED BluRay version.

